issue.title: Music should start playing when they click on "Play Radio"
issue.body:
Rather than having music start playing when they click on a song for an artist, it should behave more like a radio. Music should begin playing when they click "Play Radio"

Default: Could be the first radio station, first artist, first song, but ...
Ideally: We would save the last viewed radio station for each user. When they click on "Play Radio", it should play from that station.

issue.title: Implement spotify sdk for streaming music
issue.body:
Currently streaming songs doesn't work.
Lets use the spotify SDK to stream music.
